#use wml::debian::consultant name="TecVD"

<p>
TecVD is specialized in security and open source implementations, handles 
installation and configuration, systems integration, disaster recovery and 
network architecture on GNU/Linux (overcoat Debian), OpenBSD and FreeBSD.
</p>

<p>
Some topics in our expertise:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>
	  Security audit (vulnerability test, WLAN, perimetral security,
	  encryption, etc.)
	</li>
	<li>
	  Security implementations (firewall, IDS/IPS, VPNs, antivirus,
	  access control, encryption, etc.)
	</li>
	<li>Security management (Security Plan, etc.)</li>
	<li>Functional and economic analysis in migrations</li>
	<li>Workstations and server migrations</li>
	<li>Server consolidation and virtualization</li>
	<li>
	  Integration for heterogeneous environments (Windows, GNU/Linux,
	  UNIX, xBSD, Mac, etc.) in mixed mode
	</li>
</ul>

<p>
Also, we have network appliances for security (firewall, IDS, proxy, 
captive portal, etc.), like Tseg series, and network services (fax server, 
files and printers server, directory server, mail server, etc.), like Tcor 
series.
</p>
